\m
\v 16 Seg ket twenti powa (24) elda yepiya re towaina w…®p omnenapu kasand omn…®ki wekenonj, ton God…®m w…®p…®nd kumsos b'amk…®to …® ket as …®rouk…®to …® d…®de ket God…®nd yewangayo.  
\v 17 ∆ó ton ket God…®nd yesoureno da,  
\q1 ‚ÄúKomkesa Dandam R…®g…®b R…®ga, sowa Yonggyam God  
