\v 1 ∆ó seben (7) besen k…®ma seben (7) aneru wa w…®ng…®r…®nd y…®pa anerut ikonj kor p…®lwa, …® nomnonj da, ‚ÄúMetk…®m ayo! Kon …®ta motouyaen ukoi yiyagyiyag iyenapu konggamna b'…®sag…®ka gatab yeto re omiti w…®bneneny jogjog ny…® kumb…®nd.  
